Each now has 6 unique thematically-named moves reflecting the skill's identity (e.g., 封山劍法 has mountain-themed moves like「峰回路轉」「空山鳥語」, 六亂劍法 has chaos-themed moves like「亂花迷眼」「顛倒乾坤」).
