## Implemented Quests

### Quest 1: 搬箱子打工 (Crate Carrying) — `foreman.c`
- **Location**: 貨棧 (`store.c`)
- **Flow**: Say "打工" → pick up crates → `load crate into wagon` → say "工錢" to collect
- **First-time bonus**: Load 3+ crates (75+ coins) → extra 100 coins + 50 quest XP
- **Flag**: `quest/foreman_crate_done`

### Quest 2: 尋女任務 (Missing Daughter) — `darkrobe.c` + `girl.c`
- **Location**: 破舊莊園 (`dilapidated_manor.c`) → 破舊大宅正廳 (`ruin2.c`)
- **Flow**: Talk to 黑袍老人 (say "女兒"/"怎麼了") → sets `hairpin_quest` so girl won't attack → go to ruin2 → say "父親"/"黑袍" to girl → return to darkrobe → say "找到"/"女兒"
- **Reward**: 5 silver + 150 quest XP
- **Flag**: `quest/darkrobe_daughter_done`

### Quest 3: 拜師引導 (Apprentice Guide) — `escort.c` (NEW)
- **Location**: 廣場南 (`square_s.c`)
- **Flow**: Say "拜師"/"學武"/"門派" to 老鏢師 → get faction info + 50 coins + 30 quest XP
- **Also responds to**: specific faction questions (煉丹, 軍營, 冷梅, 血印, 苦笑)
- **Flag**: `quest/escort_guide_done`

### Pre-existing Quests (already working)
- **老乞婆** (棉襖→匕首→西瓜): 200 quest XP + rosary + white robe
- **送信** (postman→herbalist): 100 quest XP + 100 coins

### Files Modified
- `mudlib/d/snow/npc/foreman.c` — added quest bonus + "打工" dialogue
- `mudlib/d/snow/npc/darkrobe.c` — complete quest flow with reward
- `mudlib/d/snow/npc/girl.c` — responds to father mention for darkrobe quest
- `mudlib/d/snow/square_s.c` — loads escort NPC

### Files Created
- `mudlib/d/snow/npc/escort.c` — new apprentice guide NPC
